1. MySql DB Connection:

        "DB": {
            "gearhost": "server=den1.mysql4.gear.host;port=3306;database=samwiseknights;user idsamwiseknights;  password=Ep4Q?    VGCx63!"
          }



2. Follows the Pattern...

          "DB": {
        "gearhost": "server= { server name } ;port=3306;database= { database name } ;user id={ database name } ;    password= { password }"
          }



3. And is Copied into...

        appsettings.Development.json & appsettings.json



4. Which are added to .gitignore

        appsettings.*
            .vscode



5. Add Packages through "Nuget"

        *ctrl* 'p' => ">nuget" => "Add Package" => "CodeWorks.Auth0Provider", "microsoft.aspnetcore.authentication.jwtbearer", "MySqlConnector", & "Dapper"
                Look up all downloaded packages in "___projectName.csproj"